〈'''唯一信念'''〉<ref>{{cite AV media |title=老菸槍雙人組與菲比萊恩 The Chainsmokers ft. Phoebe Ryan - 唯一信念 All We Know 中文字幕 MV |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPXheeZUy5Q |language=zh |deadurl=no |date=2016-12-08 |accessdate=2021-01-25 |publisher=台灣索尼音樂 Sony Music Taiwan YouTube 頻道 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210125140029/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPXheeZUy5Q |archivedate=2021-01-25 }} {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20210125140029/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPXheeZUy5Q |date=2021-01-25 }}</ref>（{{lang-en|"All We Know"}}）是美国[[唱片骑师|DJ]]双人组[[烟鬼组合|烟鬼组合]]的单曲。歌曲由安德鲁·塔加特和[[菲比·瑞安|菲比·瑞安]]演唱，并于2016年9月29日通过{{tsl|en|Disruptor Records|破坏者唱片}}和[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]正式发行<ref>{{cite web|url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/all-we-know-feat.-phoebe-ryan/id1157626056|title = All We Know (feat. Phoebe Ryan) - Single by The Chainsmokers on Apple Music|access-date = 2016-09-30|date = 2016-09-30|work = [[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (US)|archive-date = 2016-10-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161002182029/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/all-we-know-feat.-phoebe-ryan/id1157626056|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7526386/the-chainsmokers-all-we-know-phoebe-ryan|title=The Chainsmokers Release New Single 'All We Know' Feat. Phoebe Ryan: Listen|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|last=Bein|first=Kat|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2016-10-05|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011135442/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7526386/the-chainsmokers-all-we-know-phoebe-ryan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景和作曲==
烟鬼组合在谈到〈唯一信念〉时说：“歌曲讲述了人际关系的艰难，但绝不要放弃为你赴汤蹈火的人。”<ref name="MTV" />

歌曲采用[[C大调|C大调]]，[[速度_(音乐)|速度]]为90bpm，和弦在C、F{{small|sus2}}和AM之间交替，人声跨度为G<sub>3</sub>到A<sub>4</sub><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0169005|title=The Chainsmokers feat. Phoebe Ryan "All We Know" Sheet Music in C Major (transposable)|website=Musicnotes|accessdate=2016-10-01|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022200617/http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0169005|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌词由塔加特和瑞典歌曲创作双人组SHY谱写，SHY包括萨拉·赫耶斯特罗姆（Sara Hjellström）和尼罗布·伊斯兰（Nirob Islam）（分别称{{tsl|en|Shy Martin|夏伊·马丁}}和夏伊·诺迪），烟鬼组合负责歌曲制作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thismustbepop.com/2016/10/31/kream-clara-mae-taped-up-heart/|title=Song of the Week: KREAM ft. Clara Mae – Taped Up Heart|website=This Must Be Pop|date=2016-10-31|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107092717/http://www.thismustbepop.com/2016/10/31/kream-clara-mae-taped-up-heart/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评价==
《{{tsl|en|Teen Vogue|时尚手册}}》的伊西斯·布里奥尼斯（Isis Briones）认为“在你觉得节拍朗朗上口时，这首歌探讨了一种比想和前任复合更糟糕的情况：一段日渐冷淡的关系。两位DJ打开了一扇和许多人有关的情感之门。尽管最初的歌词可能很悲惨，但在听了剩余部分后，歌曲会给你最暖心的感觉。”<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.teenvogue.com/story/the-chainsmokers-phoebe-ryan-all-we-know|title = The Chainsmokers New Song 'All We Know' Featuring Phoebe Ryan Is Out Now - Teen Vogue|last = Briones|first = Isis|access-date = 2016-09-30|date = 2016-09-30|work = {{tsl|en|Teen Vogue||Teen Vogue}}|archive-date = 2016-10-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161003092444/http://www.teenvogue.com/story/the-chainsmokers-phoebe-ryan-all-we-know|dead-url = no}}</ref>《{{tsl|en|Idolator (website)|Idolator}}》网站的迈克·瓦斯（Mike Wass）称“（〈唯一信念〉）继承了〈[[靠近我_(老菸槍雙人組歌曲)|靠近]]〉”，并说道“几乎就像烟鬼组合采用了〈靠近〉并加以完善，比较没有新意，但也是明智之举。”<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.idolator.com/7647084/chainsmokers-phoebe-ryan-all-we-know-full-song|title = The Chainsmokers and Phoebe Ryan's 'All We Know' - Idolator|last = Wass|first = Mike|access-date = 2016-09-30|date = 2016-09-29|work = {{tsl|en|Idolator (website)||Idolator}}|archive-date = 2020-11-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103040212/https://www.idolator.com/7647084/chainsmokers-phoebe-ryan-all-we-know-full-song|dead-url = no}}</ref>《[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]》的迪帕·拉克什敏（Deepa Lakshmin）认为这是一首“苦乐参半的歌曲，讲述了一段不太顺利的恋情”，并称“基本上是〈靠近〉的续作。”<ref name="MTV">{{cite web|url = http://www.mtv.com/news/2938001/chainsmokers-all-we-know-phoebe-ryan/|title = The Chainsmokers' New Song Is Basically A Sequel To 'Closer' - MTV|last = Lakshmin|first = Deepa|access-date = 2016-09-30|date = 2016-09-29|work = [[音樂電視網|MTV]]|archive-date = 2017-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170222211144/http://www.mtv.com/news/2938001/chainsmokers-all-we-know-phoebe-ryan/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==音乐视频==
〈唯一信念〉的音乐视频由罗里·克雷默（Rory Kramer）执导，2016年11月17日发布于[[YouTube|YouTube]]。烟鬼组合在视频中客串顾客，[[菲比·瑞安|菲比·瑞安]]客串收银员。视频开始，一男子（凯西·戴德里克（Casey Deidrick）饰）在接到一通令人绝望的电话后从女友（乔斯琳·阿尔博尔（Jocelin Albor）饰）家中逃了出来。他在商店买了瓶酒，然后砸碎了瓶子，扔掉了手机并掀翻了垃圾桶。他感到很疲惫，在太阳快要升起时搭便车离开了城市。视频以男子在山路上行走的镜头作为结尾，并回切了昨晚事件的片段，最终他在山顶见到了女友<ref name="YTB">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7mWQ38SpEf8|title=The Chainsmokers - All We Know (Official Video) ft. Phoebe Ryan|work=YouTube|date=2016-11-17|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830040154/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7mWQ38SpEf8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

视频通过在凯西的腰间绑上摄像头来进行录制<ref name="YTB" />。

